  <thing id="arS2ChaEgo" name="Changeling Egoist" description="A changeling’s aptitude at reshaping his body makes him naturally inclined toward psionic powers that perform similar tasks, such as those of the psychometabolism discipline. The egoist—a psion who specializes in psychometabolic powers—is an avenue often pursued by psionic changelings; such characters are well-known for their superior mastery of the discipline.\n\n{b}Pathfinder:{/b} This archetype is desgined to work with the Psion class from Ulatimate Psionics.\n\nTODO: Implement this fully when the packs all become one." compset="ClassVary" uniqueness="unique">
